-- Canada to Make Announcement About Telecom Industry
-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 2012-03-14T17:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-14/canada-to-make-announcement-about-telecom-industry-at-4-p-m-1-.html
Canadian Industry Minister
Christian Paradis will make an announcement today about the
telecommunications industry. Paradis will make a statement
around 4 p.m., an advisory from his office said.  While the advisory provides no details,  Canada  has been
preparing to issue rules that will govern its next auction of
wireless spectrum. Canada has also been studying changes to
foreign ownership rules in the sector.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Theophilos Argitis in Ottawa at 
 targitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  